desmoj.extensions.visualization2d.engine.model

Class Model

  • java.lang.Object
    • desmoj.extensions.visualization2d.engine.model.Model

  • public class Model
extends java.lang.Object
    Model manages the creation and update of every animation-object. the animation-objects are accessable over a static animation.orga.ClassContent hashtable.
